<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, August 28 (Xinhua) -- Romanian head coach Victor
Piturca dropped veteran defender Daniel Prodan from the 18-man
squad for next week's European championship qualifier against
Liechtenstein.
</P>
<P>
The Rangers defender had been included in the initial 25-man
lineup.
</P>
<P>
Romania faces Liechtenstein at home on September 2 and Germany
in Malta three days later.
</P>
