<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 28 (Xinhua) -- China's real estate index was
103.75 points in July, 0.81 points higher than in the January-June
period, the State Statistics Bureau and the China Business Climate
Monitoring Center reported today.
</P>
<P>
