<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Closes Sharply Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 28 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
slumped 76 HK dollars to close at 2,508 HK dollars a tael on
Friday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers
in Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 271.71 U.S. dollars a troy
ounce, 8.3 U.S. dollars down from the previous close at Friday's
exchange rate of one U.S. dollar to 7.7480 HK dollars. 
</P>
